(162, 1, '2015-11-13 04:43:11', '2015-11-13 04:43:11', 'Pop this style into the header (or wherever you need it):\n<pre>.embed-container { \n  position: relative; \n  padding-bottom: 56.25%; \n  height: 0; \n  overflow: hidden; \n  max-width: 100%; \n} \n\n.embed-container iframe, \n.embed-container object, \n.embed-container embed { \n  position: absolute; \n  top: 0; \n  left: 0; \n  width: 100%; \n  height: 100%; \n}\n</pre>\n&nbsp;\n\nThen add the iFrame like normal but remove the width and height attributes and wrap it in a &lt;div&gt; element using the .embed-container class:\n<div>\n<pre>&lt;div class=''embed-container''&gt;\n    &lt;iframe src=''https://www.youtube.com/embed/[youtube_video_id]'' frameborder=''0'' allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;</pre>\n</div>', 'Galaxy clusters and Gravitational Lensing', 'Generally, three methods are in reasonable agreement, that clusters contain much more matter than suggested by the visible components of galaxies and gas.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '159-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-11-13 04:43:11', '2015-11-13 04:43:11', '', 159, 'http://allyourbase.fisheyeconsulting.com/159-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(163, 1, '2015-11-03 22:38:13', '2015-11-03 22:38:13', '<code>\r\n.embed-container { position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden; max-width: 100%; }\r\n.embed-container iframe, .embed-container object, .embed-container embed { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; }\r\n</code>\r\n', 'Embedded YouTube Video with Fluid Width', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '159-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-11-03 22:38:13', '2015-11-03 22:38:13', '', 159, 'http://allyourbase.fisheyeconsulting.com/159-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(164, 1, '2015-11-03 22:39:03', '2015-11-03 22:39:03', '<code>\r\n.embed-container { position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden; max-width: 100%; }\r\n.embed-container iframe, .embed-container object, .embed-container embed { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; }\r\n</code>', 'Embed YouTube Videos with Fluid Width', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '159-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-11-03 22:39:03', '2015-11-03 22:39:03', '', 159, 'http://allyourbase.fisheyeconsulting.com/159-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(165, 1, '2015-11-03 22:43:54', '2015-11-03 22:43:54', '<p>Pop this style into the header (or wherever you need it)</p>\r\n<code>.embed-container { position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden; max-width: 100%; } .embed-container iframe, .embed-container object, .embed-container embed { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; }\r\n</code>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Then add the iFrame like normal but remove the width and height attributes and wrap it in a <div> element using the .embed-container class.</p>\r\n<code><div class=''embed-container''><iframe src=''https://www.youtube.com/embed/[youtube_video_id]'' frameborder=''0'' allowfullscreen></iframe></div></code>\r\n', 'Embed YouTube Videos with Fluid Width', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '159-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-11-03 22:43:54', '2015-11-03 22:43:54', '', 159, 'http://allyourbase.fisheyeconsulting.com/159-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(166, 1, '2015-11-03 22:44:56', '2015-11-03 22:44:56', 'Pop this style into the header (or wherever you need it)\r\n\r\n<code>.embed-container { position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden; max-width: 100%; } .embed-container iframe, .embed-container object, .embed-container embed { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; }</code>\r\n\r\nThen add the iFrame like normal but remove the width and height attributes and wrap it in a\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nelement using the .embed-container class.\r\n\r\n<code>&lt;div class=''embed-container''&gt;&lt;iframe src=''https://www.youtube.com/embed/x1RIErXCF6s'' frameborder=''0'' allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Embed YouTube Videos with Fluid Width', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '159-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-11-03 22:44:56', '2015-11-03 22:44:56', '', 159, 'http://allyourbase.fisheyeconsulting.com/159-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
